{"tid":1379853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於罷工有少少建議","createTime":"2019-07-29T01:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T04:20:34.000Z","uid":27436,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"238227585c91b609fac00d8db3d58f1dcfecc037","tid":1379853,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:01:19.000Z","msg":"我從來未開過po 亦都比較少留言 但有少少建議<br />\n關於罷工 我諗就算如連登仔 其實都仲諗緊<br />\n因為大家都係打工仔 仲驚冇左份工 驚上司唔認可 驚身邊冇同事一齊罷<br />\n到時喺職場上會受到壓力<br />\n<br />\n但如果我地得到上司認可 我認為絕對有機會令更多人願意罷工<br />\n而我地一直以黎做嘅宣傳只限於社交媒體 連登圍爐<br />\n咁其實係處於被動<br />\n因為大部分人都只會睇完就算<br />\n最多都係讚好<br />\n讚好完 咪好實際咁諗&rdquo;都係不了，廢事俾同事笑&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n所以我地要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">主動出擊</span><br />\n直接send email邀請各大公司 各大政府部門同機構罷工<br />\nSend俾佢地老細 做到<span style=\"font-size: large;\">由上而下</span>嘅策略<br />\n相信佢地嘅email唔會難搵<br />\n政府部門可以搵gov. directory<br />\n私人公司都可以上網站搵或靠各位連登仔俾料<br />\n<br />\n麻煩文宣組 寫封靚嘅email<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以好general 亦可以因應早前各行各界 各政府部門嘅公開信作引子<br />\n希望可以說服到較高層嘅人士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>是"},{"pid":"4aa5076665fdde24c24f9f1d760564e3826f7db1","tid":1379853,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:05:08.000Z","msg":"屌 多左個是字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601b01089d0d25c58662850530d3178f50135594","tid":1379853,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:26:38.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ddb95fe22c10b77077e024384df3694b8ad00aa","tid":1379853,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:26:57.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0c912faa66a9fd393aa7af96586b8ba50d1367","tid":1379853,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:27:07.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c460633add607552e3c132caec2ae5f50c41c9e","tid":1379853,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:19:38.000Z","msg":"十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8531c97abdc2792a9eb8fe60fda9cd3e22d65764","tid":1379853,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:19:49.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"a9ad37a95542bd8a48db2fdec06800275db46d17","tid":1379853,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:20:01.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1e597d52c0be787bc87cb4c8089592c4dabcb26b","tid":1379853,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:20:12.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"e4003017da11fbae4d3884641c5d373f8222e315","tid":1379853,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:20:24.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"498c479e0529adaa1fd4e7ad85a03c2c57aa055c","tid":1379853,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:20:34.000Z","msg":"5"}]}